metadata.synopsis: Ninefingers congratulates her Guild on the victory over the Zhent

0.speaker: Nine-Fingers Keene
0.text: That's enough gawking, all. Back to work - there's a mess needs cleaning up here.
0.context: NodeContext: Calling out to her assembled Guild members as the battle winds down and she goes back to her office. Casual - the Zhentarim she just slaughtered aren't even worth a second thought.
